---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageHead from "../../components/PageHead.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="15-Minute Machine Knitting Help | Knit it Now"
  description="Get expert machine knitting help in just 15 minutes. Quick, focused Zoom sessions to get unstuck and move forward."
>
  <div class="page-wrap quick-help-page-wrap">
    <PageHead
      
      hideTitle
    />

    <!-- Hero: 2-col layout — left = headline, copy, CTAs; right = image placeholder -->
    <section class="quick-help-hero">
      <div class="quick-help-hero__content">
        <h1 class="quick-help-hero__headline">Knit it Now Quick Help</h1>
        <p class="quick-help-hero__subhead">Stop the Frustration: Get clear answers without hours of searching.
          <p>
          When your machine isn't cooperating or a project suddenly stops making sense, it's easy to feel stuck.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sometimes you don't need a full class or a long lesson. You just need a little guidance to figure out what's going wrong—or what to do next.
        </p>
        <p>
          These short 15-minute Zoom sessions are designed to give you quick, focused guidance so you can move forward again with confidence.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is the fastest way to get personal help without committing to a full class or coaching program.
        </p>
        <p class="quick-help-reassurance">
          Direct help from Sue, focused on your question, your project, and your next step.
        </p>
        <div class="quick-help-hero__ctas">
          <a href="#" class="quick-help-btn quick-help-btn--primary">Book a Session</a>
          <a href="#" class="quick-help-btn quick-help-btn--secondary">Buy the 4-Session Package</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quick-help-image-placeholder quick-help-image-placeholder--hero" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>Knitting Machine / Workspace Image</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="kbm-divider" />

    <!-- What We Can Work On -->
    <section class="quick-help-section">
      <h2>What We Can Work On</h2>
      <p class="quick-help-section__intro">Your session can focus on one specific question or problem, such as:</p>
      <ul class="quick-help-list">
        <li>understanding part of a knitting pattern</li>
        <li>troubleshooting a machine issue</li>
        <li>getting started on a new project</li>
        <li>guidance using DesignaKnit</li>
        <li>figuring out the next step in your knitting</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="quick-help-section__outro">The goal is simple: clarity and confidence so you can keep knitting.</p>
    </section>

    <hr class="kbm-divider" />

    <!-- How the Sessions Work -->
    <section class="quick-help-section">
      <h2>How the Sessions Work</h2>
      <p>
        To make the most of our time together, every session begins with a short intake form.
      </p>
      <p>
        This allows you to describe exactly what you need help with before the call, so we can spend the full session solving the problem instead of gathering details.
      </p>
      <div class="quick-help-steps">
        <div class="quick-help-step">
          <span class="quick-help-step__num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
          <div class="quick-help-step__body">
            <strong>Purchase your session</strong>
            <p>Choose a single session or a session package.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-help-step">
          <span class="quick-help-step__num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
          <div class="quick-help-step__body">
            <strong>Complete the intake form</strong>
            <p>Tell me about your machine, your project, and the question you want help with.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-help-step">
          <span class="quick-help-step__num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
          <div class="quick-help-step__body">
            <strong>Schedule your Zoom session</strong>
            <p>After purchasing, you'll complete the intake form and we'll schedule a time that works for both of us.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-help-step">
          <span class="quick-help-step__num" aria-hidden="true">4</span>
          <div class="quick-help-step__body">
            <strong>Meet for 15 minutes</strong>
            <p>We'll focus on your question and help you move forward with clear next steps.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="kbm-divider" />

    <!-- Stuck Happens to Everyone -->
    <section class="quick-help-section quick-help-empathy">
      <h2>Stuck Happens to Everyone</h2>
      <p>
        Even experienced machine knitters run into moments where something just isn't working.
      </p>
      <p>
        Instead of spending hours trying to figure it out alone, a quick conversation can often make the next step clear again.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="kbm-divider" />

    <!-- Session Options -->
    <section class="quick-help-section quick-help-pricing-wrap">
      <h2>Session Options</h2>
      <div class="quick-help-cards">
        <div class="quick-help-card">
          <h3 class="quick-help-card__title">Single Session</h3>
          <p class="quick-help-card__subtitle">15-Minute Zoom Consultation</p>
          <p class="quick-help-card__body">
            Perfect if you have one specific question or need quick troubleshooting help.
          </p>
          <p class="quick-help-card__price">$59.99</p>
          <a href="#" class="quick-help-btn quick-help-btn--primary">Book a Session</a>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-help-card quick-help-card--featured">
          <h3 class="quick-help-card__title">Four-Session Package</h3>
          <p class="quick-help-card__subtitle">Four 15-Minute Zoom Sessions</p>
          <p class="quick-help-card__body">
            If you're working through a project or learning something new, the package allows you to schedule sessions when you need them.
          </p>
          <p class="quick-help-card__price">$199.99</p>
          <p class="quick-help-card__save">Save $40 compared to purchasing sessions individually.</p>
          <a href="#" class="quick-help-btn quick-help-btn--primary">Buy the 4-Session Package</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="kbm-divider" />

    <!-- Work With Sue -->
    <section class="quick-help-section quick-help-about">
      <h2>Work With Sue</h2>
      <div class="quick-help-about__grid">
        <div class="quick-help-image-placeholder quick-help-image-placeholder--sue" aria-hidden="true">
          <span>Sue Photo Placeholder</span>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-help-about__text">
          <p>
            I've spent more than 15 years helping machine knitters solve problems, finish projects, and feel more confident using their machines.
          </p>
          <p>
            Sometimes the biggest challenge isn't learning something new — it's simply figuring out what's going wrong.
          </p>
          <p>
            These short sessions are designed to help you quickly identify the issue, understand your next step, and move forward with your knitting.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="kbm-divider" />

    <!-- Making the Most of Your Session -->
    <section class="quick-help-section">
      <h2>Making the Most of Your Session</h2>
      <p>These sessions work best when we focus on one main topic or question.</p>
      <ul class="quick-help-list">
        <li>complete the intake form</li>
        <li>include photos if helpful</li>
        <li>have your machine or project nearby during the call</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This helps us use the full time solving your problem and getting you back to knitting.</p>
    </section>

    <hr class="kbm-divider" />

    <!-- A Quick Note -->
    <section class="quick-help-section">
      <h2>A Quick Note</h2>
      <p>
        These sessions are designed for focused guidance and troubleshooting rather than full lessons or extended project instruction.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you're unsure whether your question is a good fit, feel free to reach out and ask.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="kbm-divider" />

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="quick-help-section quick-help-cta">
      <h2>Ready to Get Unstuck?</h2>
      <p>
        Sometimes a few minutes of guidance can save hours of frustration.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you're stuck on a problem or unsure what to do next, a quick session may be exactly what you need.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Choose your session and let's get you moving forward again.</strong></p>
      <div class="quick-help-cta-buttons">
        <a href="#" class="quick-help-btn quick-help-btn--primary">Book a Session</a>
        <a href="#" class="quick-help-btn quick-help-btn--secondary">Buy the 4-Session Package</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Layout already supplies header clearance; keep minimal top padding */
  .quick-help-page-wrap.page-wrap {
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  /* ----- Hero ----- */
  .quick-help-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .quick-help-hero__content {
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .quick-help-hero__headline {
    font-size: var(--text-xxl);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--kbm-green);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .quick-help-hero__subhead {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: #4a5568;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .quick-help-hero__content > p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .quick-help-reassurance {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--kbm-green);
    margin-top: 0.25rem !important;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem !important;
  }

  .quick-help-hero__ctas {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* Hero + Sue image placeholders */
  .quick-help-image-placeholder {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(199, 216, 164, 0.22) 0%, rgba(229, 232, 224, 0.35) 100%);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(82, 104, 45, 0.35);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(82, 104, 45, 0.06);
  }

  .quick-help-image-placeholder span {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #6b7280;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .quick-help-image-placeholder--hero {
    min-height: 280px;
  }

  .quick-help-image-placeholder--sue {
    min-height: 200px;
    max-width: 280px;
  }

  /* ----- Sections ----- */
  .quick-help-section {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .quick-help-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--kbm-green);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .quick-help-section p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .quick-help-section__intro,
  .quick-help-section__outro {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .quick-help-list {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 1.5rem;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .quick-help-list li {
    position: relative;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .quick-help-list li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.5em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--kbm-green);
  }

  .quick-help-section li::marker {
    color: var(--kbm-green);
  }

  /* Empathy section */
  .quick-help-empathy {
    background: rgba(82, 104, 45, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid var(--ring);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
  }

  .quick-help-empathy p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ----- How It Works steps ----- */
  .quick-help-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
  }

  .quick-help-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--ring);
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  .quick-help-step__num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--kbm-green);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .quick-help-step__body strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    color: var(--kbm-green);
  }

  .quick-help-step__body p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ----- Pricing ----- */
  .quick-help-pricing-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(199, 216, 164, 0.12) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(82, 104, 45, 0.12);
  }

  .quick-help-pricing-wrap h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .quick-help-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .quick-help-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 2px solid var(--ring);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: stretch;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .quick-help-card--featured {
    border-color: var(--kbm-green);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(82, 104, 45, 0.14);
  }

  .quick-help-card__title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--kbm-green);
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
  }

  .quick-help-card__subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: #6b7280;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .quick-help-card__body {
    flex: 1;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .quick-help-card__price {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--kbm-green);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .quick-help-card__save {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  /* ----- Work With Sue ----- */
  .quick-help-about__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .quick-help-about__text p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .quick-help-about__text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ----- Buttons ----- */
  .quick-help-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.08s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .quick-help-btn--primary {
    background-color: var(--kbm-green);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--kbm-green);
  }

  .quick-help-btn--primary:hover {
    background-color: var(--kbm-green-hover);
    border-color: var(--kbm-green-hover);
  }

  .quick-help-btn--secondary {
    background-color: #fff;
    color: var(--kbm-green);
    border-color: var(--kbm-green);
  }

  .quick-help-btn--secondary:hover {
    background-color: rgba(82, 104, 45, 0.08);
  }

  .quick-help-cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .quick-help-cta h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .quick-help-cta p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* ----- Responsive ----- */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .quick-help-hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .quick-help-hero__ctas {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .quick-help-hero__ctas .quick-help-btn {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .quick-help-image-placeholder--hero {
      min-height: 220px;
    }

    .quick-help-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .quick-help-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .quick-help-about__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .quick-help-image-placeholder--sue {
      max-width: 100%;
      min-height: 180px;
    }

    .quick-help-cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .quick-help-cta-buttons .quick-help-btn {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .quick-help-pricing-wrap {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
